#Mojaloop Architecture Design


##API Layer (FSPIOP API)
Standard interface used by all DFSPs to communicate.

##Switch
Routes messages between DFSPs.

##Account Lookup Service (ALS)
Resolves recipient details (e.g., phone → account).

##Quotes Service
Calculates fees and validates if a transaction can proceed.

##Transfers Service
Handles transaction execution and state management.

##Position / Central Ledger
Tracks balances of each DFSP in real time.

##Settlement Service
Handles final settlement between DFSPs.
